class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"bp\">‚Üí</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">f</span> <span class=\"bp\">‚àò</span> <span class=\"n\">u</span> <span class=\"bp\">‚ü∂</span> <span class=\"n\">b</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span>\n<span class=\"kd\">begin</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">refine</span> <span class=\"o\">‚ü®</span><span class=\"bp\">Œª</span> <span class=\"n\">hf</span> <span class=\"n\">u</span> <span class=\"n\">hu</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">hf.comp</span> <span class=\"n\">hu</span><span class=\"o\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"bp\">Œª</span> <span class=\"n\">h</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"o\">((</span><span class=\"n\">nhds_basis_closeds</span> <span class=\"n\">_</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">tendsto_iff</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">nhds_basis_closeds</span> <span class=\"n\">_</span><span class=\"o\">))</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"mi\">2</span> <span class=\"n\">_</span><span class=\"o\">‚ü©,</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">rintro</span> <span class=\"n\">s</span> <span class=\"o\">‚ü®</span><span class=\"n\">hbs</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">hsc</span><span class=\"o\">‚ü©,</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">refine</span> <span class=\"o\">‚ü®</span><span class=\"n\">closure</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">f</span> <span class=\"bp\">‚Åª¬π'</span> <span class=\"n\">s</span><span class=\"o\">),</span> <span class=\"o\">‚ü®</span><span class=\"n\">mt</span> <span class=\"n\">_</span> <span class=\"n\">hbs</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">is_closed_closure</span><span class=\"o\">‚ü©,</span> <span class=\"bp\">Œª</span> <span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">mt</span> <span class=\"bp\">$</span> <span class=\"bp\">Œª</span> <span class=\"n\">hx</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">subset_closure</span> <span class=\"n\">hx</span><span class=\"o\">‚ü©,</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">rw</span> <span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"bp\">‚Üê</span> <span class=\"n\">sequential_space.sequential_closure_eq_closure</span><span class=\"o\">],</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">rintro</span> <span class=\"o\">‚ü®</span><span class=\"n\">u</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">hus</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">hu</span><span class=\"o\">‚ü©,</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">exact</span> <span class=\"n\">hsc.mem_of_tendsto</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">h</span> <span class=\"n\">u</span> <span class=\"n\">hu</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">eventually_of_forall</span> <span class=\"n\">hus</span><span class=\"o\">)</span>\n<span class=\"kd\">end</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
